ComicInfo.Title: Two Heads Are Better Than---; Teenage Movie Monsters; Monday Morning, Rather Early; Gigglin's Island the Motion Picture; One Knight at the White House; The Job; Forgotten Funnies!; Yucktales; Football Game; One Electrifying Morning at the State Pen; Rangey Loner; Toilet Zone; One Shots; My Two Duds!; You Know You're a Couch Potato When...; Leonerd Part 6; The Evolution of the Movie Kiss!; One Shots
ComicInfo.Summary:
Men punch a timeclock to take turns putting their fingers into a dike.
Hudd and Dini tunnel into the middle of a football game where the players tackle them.
The Rangey Loner is asked to help defend a woman's chickens from werewolves, but the werewolves are themselves eaten by the Talking Blob.
